Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:02.70,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Terrible, terrible, awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:07.13,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I've got terrible bad news for everyone!\NOK, listen up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:15.00,forest title KB,,0,0,0,,FABLES \N of the\NGREEN FOREST
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:15.00,forest ep title C,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&HFFFFFF&}Today's episode:\N{\c&H25CE1D&}"The straw hat monster"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:22.70,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Terrible, terrible!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:26.57,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Johnny, it's cruel!\NCould anything be more cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:28.28,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Sammy, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:31.23,forest default C,,0,0,0,,It's that guy, Reddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:32.68,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Who, Reddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:34.52,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Chatterer is the one to be pitied,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:38.42,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I'm so mad, so mad\NI just can't stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:41.46,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I must tell everyone about it!\NTerrible, terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:43.64,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Terrible, terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:50.95,forest default C,,0,0,0,,He's such a scatterbrain, he left without\Ntelling us the most important part!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:53.18,forest default C,,0,0,0,,He was saying something about Chatterer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:55.05,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Let's go see!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:09.17,forest default C,,0,0,0,,It was really terrible, the fruits and nuts\Nthat I gathered... that guy, Reddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:11.93,forest default C,,0,0,0,,He took them all...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:33.59,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Look at all those nice smelling fruits!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.66,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Hmm... If the owner isn't around,\NI'll just pick 'em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:41.52,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I'm the owner, I gathered them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:48.16,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I don't want these stupid nuts anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:56.45,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sorry to have intruded!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:01:59.05,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:10.02,forest default C,,0,0,0,,- I'm amazed!\N- That Reddy is really a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:13.86,forest default C,,0,0,0,,That Reddy, oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.83,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Alright, Granny, eat, I went out and stole it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:30.75,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Hmm, now listen, Reddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.16,forest default C,,0,0,0,,What I want is a soft little rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:36.46,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Peter Rabbit that is.\NCatch him for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:40.70,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Oh, my empty stomach!\NI'm starved!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:46.25,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I know, I know, Granny,\Ntomorrow I'll catch Peter for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:48.53,forest default C,,0,0,0,,but the problem is how to catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:03:00.45,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Oh... I hear Lady Gentle Breeze's song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:20.30,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lady Gentle Breeze,\Nwill you listen to one request?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:22.47,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course, Reddy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.83,forest default C,,0,0,0,,- What can we do about this problem, Johnny...?\N- Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.59,forest default C,,0,0,0,,...we seem to really have a problem\Non our hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:40.99,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Johnny, for a while now you've been\Ngrumbling and groaning about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:44.03,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Groaning? About Reddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.63,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, Peter, you are here.\NI was looking for you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:56.68,forest default C,,0,0,0,,What is it, Gentle Breeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.13,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have a message from Reddy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.68,forest default C,,0,0,0,,- Oh...?!\N- It's from Reddy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:07.79,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said he found some tender budding carrots\Non Mr. Brown's farm,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:12.07,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and would like you to go with him\Nfirst thing tomorrow morning at sunrise.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:16.49,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Oh, budding carrots you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.31,forest default C,,0,0,0,,My favourite food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:23.56,forest default C,,0,0,0,,You're not thinking of going, are you, Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:25.09,forest default C,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:28.79,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Be careful, this might be a trick of Reddy's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:32.07,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I can't refuse\Na kind special invitation like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:33.60,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.92,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then your answer is... an OK?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:40.43,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Yes...! Tell him I'll be happy\Nto accompany him... tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:45.01,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Oh, Johnny, speak to him, stop Peter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.93,forest default C,,0,0,0,,If he goes with Reddy, he'll be eaten up!\NAren't you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.16,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid!\NBye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:10.93,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Wow, wonderful!\NIt's just like Reddy said!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.27,forest default C,,0,0,0,,How delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.45,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a delicious meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:52.07,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Good, good, good, good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:09.30,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting! OK, now let's go\Nto Mr. Brown's carrot patch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:17.66,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Peter, yesterday you promised to go with me,\Ndidn't you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.38,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Peter...!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:25.72,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Funny, no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:36.78,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Then I think I'll go by myself\Nand check the carrot patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.66,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Hmm?\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.90,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This smells like Peter!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.42,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Darn, darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:17.15,forest default C,,0,0,0,,That Peter, he fooled me!\NI'm so mad at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:20.75,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Oh!\N- Good morning, Reddy the Fox!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:24.39,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.62,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Peter asked me to see you and tell you this:{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:32.05,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he said he is truly sorry that he could not\Nmeet you this morning by the Bramble Bush.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.94,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But thinking about those tender budding carrots,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:38.54,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}made him so hungry, that he departed\Nearly this morning, before daybreak.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:42.58,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said he is really grateful to you\Nfor telling him about those carrots.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:46.30,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And those carrots were the most delicious\Nhe had ever eaten.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:52.18,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Lady Gentle Breeze, would you tell Peter this:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.58,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I'm glad the carrots were delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:59.67,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning at daybreak we'll meet again\Nand I'll take you to the sweet clover field!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:00.98,forest default C,,0,0,0,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:04.15,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I found it near the old walnut tree, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.55,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, that's fine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.63,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll relay it immediately for you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:26.37,forest narrator C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next morning, Peter set out\Nalmost two hours before daybreak.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.25,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:48.56,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Now... better hurry home\Nand get back to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.14,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I just wonder what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:10.21,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Peter always waits for me at the usual edge\Nof the Bramble Bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.26,forest default C,,0,0,0,,He never had ideas of fooling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.13,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Peter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.78,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Reddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.94,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Well, Peter...\Nlet's go to that sweet clover field!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:46.65,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I got so hungry... I couldn't wait\Nfor the sun to come up, Reddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.99,forest default C,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.11,forest default C,,0,0,0,,So I went about two hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.48,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for telling me\Nabout that new clover field!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:56.49,forest default C,,0,0,0,,You aren't mad at me, are you, Reddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.21,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:06.82,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Nothing is more pleasing than\Nto make people really cheerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:10.94,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I like to make people really happy, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:14.17,forest default C,,0,0,0,,However, I just heard about it, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:18.44,forest default C,,0,0,0,,...Mr. Brown the farmer planted some cabbage\Nin the corner of his yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:21.02,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Tommorow morning at daybreak...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:23.73,forest default C,,0,0,0,,...you want to meet here and go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.73,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Yeah...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.90,forest default C,,0,0,0,,That sounds keen!\NLet's definitely go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.97,forest default C,,0,0,0,,OK, then it's a promise this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.03,forest default C,,0,0,0,,So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.96,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I'm mad!\NI'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:11:01.58,forest default C,,0,0,0,,This time I'll go there two hours\Nbefore the sun rises,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:05.90,forest default C,,0,0,0,,then, Peter, I'm going to teach you\Nwho the smartest is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:06.90,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.98,forest lyrics C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The moon, the moon\NPlease, light up the road,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:14.26,forest lyrics C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The night's a good night,\NThe stars are twinkling,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:19.12,forest lyrics C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A happy night,\NMy friends are calling me...!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.31,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Reddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:50.10,forest default C,,0,0,0,,That R-R-Reddy is thinking:\N"H-how shall I eat him?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:53.65,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah... what do I do... n-n-now...?\NOh-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.54,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh... Reddy's face looks startled!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.89,forest default C,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just thought of something...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:25.59,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Oh! I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:47.11,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I'm getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:11.83,forest default C,,0,0,0,,- Good morning, Peter!\N- Good morning, Reddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:16.41,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Hey, well, I'm sorry to make you wait so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:19.54,forest default C,,0,0,0,,but I was actually really frightened last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.19,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Oh, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:25.54,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I ran into a hideous monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:31.43,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I was so frightened I didn't feel like\Ncoming out until the sun was out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.68,forest default C,,0,0,0,,So that's why I'm a wee bit late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.77,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Tell you what, Peter:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.90,forest default C,,0,0,0,,let's start out for the new cabbage patch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.61,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Tell me, did the monster catch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:56.19,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Uh, Reddy, uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.77,forest default C,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:03.56,forest default C,,0,0,0,,You know I can run faster than he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:07.42,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Then I decide not to go to\Nthe cabbage patch until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:12.19,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I might get caught by that monster, Reddy,\Nisn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:16.84,forest default C,,0,0,0,,And besides, I've already had my share\Nof budding cabbage plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:20.59,forest default C,,0,0,0,,The... what-what...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:24.06,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't wait till morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.91,forest default C,,0,0,0,,...so I went early last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:29.38,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Thanks for telling me about the cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:32.66,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Yes, Reddy, my heartfelt thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:39.36,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.61,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.60,forest default C,,0,0,0,,It's alright, it's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.07,forest default C,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.99,forest default C,,0,0,0,,...tell me, didn't you meet up\Nwith that terrible monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.86,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I didn't meet it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:04.45,forest default C,,0,0,0,,What in the world it's so funny with you, Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:06.74,forest default C,,0,0,0,,Tell me, I wanna laugh too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.70,forest default C,,0,0,0,,- The monster who frightened you...\N- Mhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.07,forest default C,,0,0,0,,...you won't believe it, Reddy!...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:21.15,forest default C,,0,0,0,,...was the old straw hat of Mr. Brown's son!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:25.70,forest default C,,0,0,0,,I was hiding under it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:04.50,forest credits C,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Subtitle: {\c&H1BEAED&}South Wind Subs
